<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
  body { font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1e293b; margin: 0; background: #f8fafc; }
  .wrap { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px; }
  .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 32px; }
  h1 { color: #0d9488; font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  p { line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; }
  .facts { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
  .facts td { padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-size: 14px; }
  .facts .label { color: #64748b; width: 40%; }
  .links a { color: #0d9488; text-decoration: none; }
  .footer { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 24px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>Welcome to {{ company_name }}, {{ first_name }}!</h1>
      <p>
        We're delighted you're joining us as <strong>{{ role }}</strong>. Everything is
        being set up ahead of your first day so you can hit the ground running.
      </p>

      <table class="facts">
        <tr><td class="label">Start date</td><td>{{ start_date }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="label">Role</td><td>{{ role }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="label">Manager</td><td>{{ manager_name }}</td></tr>
      </table>

      <p>
        Your welcome pack is attached — it covers your first-week schedule and key contacts.
        Calendar invites for your Day 1 induction, team intro and probation review are on
        their way separately.
      </p>

      <p class="links">
        Useful links:<br>
        Company handbook: <a href="{{ handbook_url }}">{{ handbook_url }}</a><br>
        IT support: <a href="mailto:{{ it_contact }}">{{ it_contact }}</a><br>
        People team: <a href="mailto:{{ people_contact }}">{{ people_contact }}</a>
      </p>

      <p>See you on {{ start_date }}!</p>

      <div class="footer">
        {{ company_name }} · This is an automated welcome message. Reply to {{ company_email }}
        with any questions.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
